data.description: This well maintained 3 bed, 2 bath home offers lots of desired features! Location is great for commuters and the shape of this lot provides a huge back yard, longer drive way and the cul-de-sac keeps the passer-by traffic at a minimum. The house was originally built in 2016 with hickory floors, large frog and quartz countertops but this homeowner decided added a few bonus features! A pool, trex deck and hot tub will convey to make this property the perfect home in every season. Come lay your eyes on this gem.
